VW’s Lamborghini Made Loss of 40 Million Euros, Spiegel Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-04-09T12:20:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/vw-s-lamborghini-made-loss-of-40-million-euros-spiegel-reports.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW) ’s Lamborghini unit
made a loss of almost 40 million euros ($58 million) last year,
compared with a 35 million-euro loss in 2009,  Der Spiegel  said
in a preview of a story to be published tomorrow, citing
internal VW documents.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  